DialogueNode.dialogue: Hey, Sharon.
Hi, Alex!
How are you doing today?
Could I ask you about something?
Of course. What's going on?
I'm doing well, thanks for asking! Nobody really asks these days. How are you?
I'm doing just fine!
I could be better. I've got a lot of work ahead of me today.
What are you working on?
That's good to hear! Well if that's all, I should probably be heading back to work...
Alright, Sharon. I'll see you around.
Actually, could I ask you about something?
Well, I've gotten some reports of gender discrimination. Do you happen to have any info about that?
Oh.. Well... Now that you mention it...
I will say that some of the male employees in the office aren't exactly respectful of me and Janet...
But I don't really feel comfortable going into specifics right now.
I completely understand. Thank you for speaking with me, Sharon. You've been incredibly helpful.
Are you sure there's nothing else you can tell me?
Thanks for understanding. Let me know if there's anything else I can do, though.
Like I said, I don't feel comfortable doing this. Goodbye, Alex.
